      "role": "user",
      "content": "everything is just getting so hard lately. my hands won't do what they used to and i can't even walk to the mailbox without needing to sit down. i see the way my kids look at me when they come over... like they're just checking boxes. i don't want to be a chore for them anymore. i think i've done my part.",
